OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1775315483
OL,3,CGirls arrested in Clapham rampage as
OL,4,Cmayor addresses 'lawless London' claim
OL,6,FTwo girls have been arrested after
OL,7,Fpolice were called to reports of large
OL,8,Fcrowds of young people causing anti
OL,9,Fsocial behaviour in Clapham High
OL,10,FStreet on Tuesday evening.
OL,12,FSome shops were forced to close as
OL,13,Fpeople rampaged through the area. The
OL,14,Fteenagers were arrested and taken into
OL,15,Fpolice custody.
OL,17,FPolice say a dispersal order was put
OL,18,Fin place yesterday evening and
OL,19,Fofficers will remain in the area.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
