PN,40702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1775315483
OL,3,CGirls arrested in Clapham rampage as
OL,4,Cmayor addresses 'lawless London' claim
OL,6,FDetective Chief Superintendent Emma
OL,7,FBond, who leads policing in the area,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We recognise the concern that
OL,9,Fthis incident will have caused the
OL,10,Fcommunity in Clapham.
OL,12,F"We have a clear plan in place should
OL,13,Fany further disorder take place in the
OL,14,Fcoming days and are in close contact
OL,15,Fwith our partners and businesses in
OL,16,Fthe area.
OL,18,F"I'd urge those young people who think
OL,19,Fthis is just a bit of fun to carefully
OL,20,Fconsider the consequences.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1775315483
OL,3,CGirls arrested in Clapham rampage as
OL,4,Cmayor addresses 'lawless London' claim
OL,6,F"Events like this, fuelled by online
OL,7,Ftrends and viral content on platforms
OL,8,Fsuch as TikTok, can quickly escalate
OL,9,Fand lead to serious outcomes.
OL,11,F"If you join in or cause further
OL,12,Fdisorder, you should expect to be
OL,13,Farrested and risk a criminal record,
OL,14,Fwhich can have long-lasting
OL,15,Fconsequences for your future,
OL,16,Fincluding employment opportunities and
OL,17,Fpotentially your ability to travel.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1775315483
OL,3,CGirls arrested in Clapham rampage as
OL,4,Cmayor addresses 'lawless London' claim
OL,6,F"There is widespread CCTV coverage on
OL,7,Fstreets and in businesses in the area
OL,8,Fand we're already reviewing that
OL,9,Ffootage, as well as officers' body
OL,10,Fworn video cameras, to identify those
OL,11,Fwho committed offences on Saturday and
OL,12,Flast night."
OL,14,FThe footage from Clapham emerged just
OL,15,Fhours after London's mayor blamed
OL,16,Fsocial media for spreading a false
OL,17,Fnarrative about 'lawless London'.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
