CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1775315483
OL,3,CGirls arrested in Clapham rampage as
OL,4,Cmayor addresses 'lawless London' claim
OL,6,FSadiq Khan and Met Commissioner Sir
OL,7,FMark Rowley met with the British
OL,8,FAmbassador to the US and
OL,9,Frepresentatives from Singapore, Japan,
OL,10,FUAE as well as other countries key to
OL,11,Ftourism and investment.
OL,13,FCity Hall said misleading claims about
OL,14,Fcrime levels risked putting off
OL,15,Fvisitors, students and businesses and
OL,16,FLondon remained one of the safest and
OL,17,Fmost dynamic cities to live, work and
OL,18,Fvisit.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40706
