CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1775315483
OL,3,CGirls arrested in Clapham rampage as
OL,4,Cmayor addresses 'lawless London' claim
OL,6,FAddressing the meeting Sir Sadiq Khan
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are humming as a city, but I
OL,8,Frecognise there is a perception around
OL,9,Fthe globe about London being unsafe.
OL,11,F"Of course, one crime is one crime too
OL,12,Fmany, but people are spreading false
OL,13,Fpropaganda about city because it
OL,14,Fserves their interests.
OL,16,F"So we all need to challenge the
OL,17,Fdisinformation, misinformation and
OL,18,Flies. That's why I'm so keen we share
OL,19,Fand ideas with colleagues overseas."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1775315483
OL,3,CGirls arrested in Clapham rampage as
OL,4,Cmayor addresses 'lawless London' claim
OL,6,FMr Khan said London was Europe's top
OL,7,Fdestination for tech, finance and
OL,8,Fgreen investment.
OL,10,FHe pointed to booming international
OL,11,Finterest, with record numbers of
OL,12,FAmericans coming to London to visit,
OL,13,Fstudy, work and invest.
OL,15,FThe city has also attracted major
OL,16,Fbacking from global companies
OL,17,Fincluding JP Morgan, Google, Apple and
OL,18,FOpenAI reinforcing its status as a
OL,19,Fleading business hub.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
