FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1775315483
OL,3,CGirls arrested in Clapham rampage as
OL,4,Cmayor addresses 'lawless London' claim
OL,6,FResponding to the scenes in Clapham,
OL,7,FSadiq Khan said: "The appalling scenes
OL,8,Fin Clapham in recent days are
OL,9,Fabsolutely unacceptable and those
OL,10,Fresponsible will face the full force
OL,11,Fof the law.
OL,13,F"Two arrests have been made and the
OL,14,FMet is continuing to investigate.
OL,16,F"There will be an increased police
OL,17,Fpresence in the area in the coming
OL,18,Fdays, with officers providing support
OL,19,Fand reassurance to residents and
OL,20,Fbusinesses."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
